          <p>Your private access link is in that email. If you don't see it within a few minutes, check your spam folder and add rose@thedrivenceo.com to your contacts so future emails land safely.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num"><span>2</span></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Start from Episode 1 — it sets everything up</h3>
          <p>Each episode is 10–15 minutes. No guests, no sponsors, no filler. You can jump around but Episode 1 gives you the full context for everything that follows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num"><span>3</span></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Hit reply when something lands</h3>
          <p>Rose reads every email. If an episode makes you think "that's exactly where I'm stuck" — reply and tell her. That conversation might be the most useful thing you do today.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



<footer>
  <span class="f-logo">© 2026 The Driven CEO LLC</span>
  <div class="f-links"><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a><a href="#">Terms</a></div>
</footer>

